HEADWORD: Benthos
<hw>Ben"thos</hw> <pr>(b⟦ecr⟧n"th⟦ocr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>be`nqos</grk> depth of the sea.]</ety> <def>The
